item.title: CVE-2023-0278|2023-02-27T15:24:40.738Z -- unknown -- geodirectory
item.description: The GeoDirectory WordPress plugin before 2.2.24 does not properly sanitise and escape a parameter before using it in a SQL statement, leading to a SQL injection exploitable by high privilege users such as admin.
